var book = {
	"name": "Amos",
	"numChapters": 9,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The words of Amos, one of the shepherds of Tekoa<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22366A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22366A\"></sup>—the vision he saw concerning Israel two years before the earthquake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22366B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22366B\"></sup> when Uzziah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22366C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22366C\"></sup> was king of Judah and Jeroboam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22366D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22366D\"></sup> son of Jehoash was king of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22366E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22366E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He said:“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> roars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22367F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22367F\"></sup> from Zionand thunders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22367G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22367G\"></sup> from Jerusalem;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22367H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22367H\"></sup>the pastures of the shepherds dry up,and the top of Carmel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22367I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22367I\"></sup> withers.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22367J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22367J\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“For three sins of Damascus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22368K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22368K\"></sup>even for four, I will not relent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22368L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22368L\"></sup>Because she threshed Gileadwith sledges having iron teeth,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will send fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22369M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22369M\"></sup> on the house of Hazael<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22369N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22369N\"></sup>that will consume the fortresses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22369O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22369O\"></sup> of Ben-Hadad.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22369P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22369P\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will break down the gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22370Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22370Q\"></sup> of Damascus;I will destroy the king who is in the Valley of Avenand the one who holds the scepter in Beth Eden.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22370R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22370R\"></sup>The people of Aram will go into exile to Kir,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22370S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22370S\"></sup>”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22370T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22370T\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“For three sins of Gaza,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22371U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22371U\"></sup>even for four, I will not relent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22371V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22371V\"></sup>Because she took captive whole communitiesand sold them to Edom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22371W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22371W\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will send fire on the walls of Gazathat will consume her fortresses.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will destroy the king of Ashdod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22373X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22373X\"></sup>and the one who holds the scepter in Ashkelon.I will turn my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22373Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22373Y\"></sup> against Ekron,till the last of the Philistines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22373Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22373Z\"></sup> are dead,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22373AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22373AA\"></sup>says the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22373AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22373AB\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“For three sins of Tyre,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22374AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22374AC\"></sup>even for four, I will not relent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22374AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22374AD\"></sup>Because she sold whole communities of captives to Edom,disregarding a treaty of brotherhood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22374AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22374AE\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will send fire on the walls of Tyrethat will consume her fortresses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22375AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22375AF\"></sup>”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“For three sins of Edom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22376AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22376AG\"></sup>even for four, I will not relent.Because he pursued his brother with a sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22376AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22376AH\"></sup>and slaughtered the women of the land,because his anger raged continuallyand his fury flamed unchecked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22376AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22376AI\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will send fire on Teman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22377AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22377AJ\"></sup>that will consume the fortresses of Bozrah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22377AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22377AK\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“For three sins of Ammon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22378AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22378AL\"></sup>even for four, I will not relent.Because he ripped open the pregnant women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22378AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22378AM\"></sup> of Gileadin order to extend his borders,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will set fire to the walls of Rabbah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22379AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22379AN\"></sup>that will consume<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22379AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22379AO\"></sup> her fortressesamid war cries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22379AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22379AP\"></sup> on the day of battle,amid violent winds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22379AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22379AQ\"></sup> on a stormy day.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Her king will go into exile,he and his officials together,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22380AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22380AR\"></sup>”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22380AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22380AS\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“For three sins of Moab,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22381A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22381A\"></sup>even for four, I will not relent.Because he burned to ashes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22381B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22381B\"></sup>the bones of Edom’s king,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will send fire on Moabthat will consume the fortresses of Kerioth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22382C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22382C\"></sup>Moab will go down in great tumultamid war cries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22382D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22382D\"></sup> and the blast of the trumpet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22382E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22382E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I will destroy her ruler<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22383F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22383F\"></sup>and kill all her officials with him,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22383G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22383G\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22383H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22383H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“For three sins of Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22384I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22384I\"></sup>even for four, I will not relent.Because they have rejected the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22384J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22384J\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and have not kept his decrees,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22384K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22384K\"></sup>because they have been led astray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22384L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22384L\"></sup> by false gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22384M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22384M\"></sup>the gods their ancestors followed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22384N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22384N\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will send fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22385O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22385O\"></sup> on Judahthat will consume the fortresses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22385P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22385P\"></sup> of Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22385Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22385Q\"></sup>”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“For three sins of Israel,even for four, I will not relent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22386R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22386R\"></sup>They sell the innocent for silver,and the needy for a pair of sandals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22386S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22386S\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They trample on the heads of the pooras on the dust of the groundand deny justice to the oppressed.Father and son use the same girland so profane my holy name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22387T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22387T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They lie down beside every altaron garments taken in pledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22388U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22388U\"></sup>In the house of their godthey drink wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22388V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22388V\"></sup> taken as fines.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22388W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22388W\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Yet I destroyed the Amorites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22389X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22389X\"></sup> before them,though they were tall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22389Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22389Y\"></sup> as the cedarsand strong as the oaks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22389Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22389Z\"></sup>I destroyed their fruit aboveand their roots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22389AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22389AA\"></sup> below.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I brought you up out of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22390AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22390AB\"></sup>and led<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22390AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22390AC\"></sup> you forty years in the wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22390AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22390AD\"></sup>to give you the land of the Amorites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22390AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22390AE\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I also raised up prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22391AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22391AF\"></sup> from among your childrenand Nazirites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22391AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22391AG\"></sup> from among your youths.Is this not true, people of Israel?”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But you made the Nazirites drink wineand commanded the prophets not to prophesy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22392AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22392AH\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Now then, I will crush youas a cart crushes when loaded with grain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22393AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22393AI\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The swift will not escape,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22394AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22394AJ\"></sup>the strong<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22394AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22394AK\"></sup> will not muster their strength,and the warrior will not save his life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22394AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22394AL\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The archer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22395AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22395AM\"></sup> will not stand his ground,the fleet-footed soldier will not get away,and the horseman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22395AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22395AN\"></sup> will not save his life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22395AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22395AO\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Even the bravest warriors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22396AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22396AP\"></sup>will flee naked on that day,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Hear this word, people of Israel, the word the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken against you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22397A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22397A\"></sup>—against the whole family I brought up out of Egypt:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22397B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22397B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“You only have I chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22398C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22398C\"></sup>of all the families of the earth;therefore I will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22398D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22398D\"></sup> youfor all your sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22398E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22398E\"></sup>”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do two walk togetherunless they have agreed to do so?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Does a lion roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22400F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22400F\"></sup> in the thicketwhen it has no prey?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22400G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22400G\"></sup>Does it growl in its denwhen it has caught nothing?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Does a bird swoop down to a trap on the groundwhen no bait<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22401H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22401H\"></sup> is there?Does a trap spring up from the groundif it has not caught anything?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When a trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22402I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22402I\"></sup> sounds in a city,do not the people tremble?When disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22402J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22402J\"></sup> comes to a city,has not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> caused it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22402K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22402K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Surely the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does nothingwithout revealing his plan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22403L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22403L\"></sup>to his servants the prophets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22403M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22403M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22404N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22404N\"></sup> has roared<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22404O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22404O\"></sup>—who will not fear?The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken—who can but prophesy?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22404P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22404P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Proclaim to the fortresses of Ashdod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22405Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22405Q\"></sup>and to the fortresses of Egypt:“Assemble yourselves on the mountains of Samaria;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22405R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22405R\"></sup>see the great unrest within herand the oppression among her people.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“They do not know how to do right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22406S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22406S\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“who store up in their fortresses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22406T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22406T\"></sup>what they have plundered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22406U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22406U\"></sup> and looted.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“An enemy will overrun your land,pull down your strongholdsand plunder your fortresses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22407V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22407V\"></sup>”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“As a shepherd rescues from the lion’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22408W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22408W\"></sup> mouthonly two leg bones or a piece of an ear,so will the Israelites living in Samaria be rescued,with only the head of a bedand a piece of fabric from a couch.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22408X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22408X\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Hear this and testify<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22409Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22409Y\"></sup> against the descendants of Jacob,” declares the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“On the day I punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22410Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22410Z\"></sup> Israel for her sins,I will destroy the altars of Bethel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22410AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22410AA\"></sup>the horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22410AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22410AB\"></sup> of the altar will be cut offand fall to the ground.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will tear down the winter house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22411AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22411AC\"></sup>along with the summer house;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22411AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22411AD\"></sup>the houses adorned with ivory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22411AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22411AE\"></sup> will be destroyedand the mansions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22411AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22411AF\"></sup> will be demolished,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22411AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22411AG\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22411AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22411AH\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Hear this word, you cows of Bashan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22412A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22412A\"></sup> on Mount Samaria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22412B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22412B\"></sup>you women who oppress the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22412C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22412C\"></sup> and crush the needy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22412D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22412D\"></sup>and say to your husbands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22412E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22412E\"></sup> “Bring us some drinks!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22412F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22412F\"></sup>”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sworn by his holiness:“The time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22413G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22413G\"></sup> will surely comewhen you will be taken away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22413H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22413H\"></sup> with hooks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22413I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22413I\"></sup>the last of you with fishhooks.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You will each go straight outthrough breaches in the wall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22414J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22414J\"></sup>and you will be cast out toward Harmon,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Go to Bethel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22415K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22415K\"></sup> and sin;go to Gilgal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22415L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22415L\"></sup> and sin yet more.Bring your sacrifices every morning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22415M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22415M\"></sup>your tithes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22415N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22415N\"></sup> every three years.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22415O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22415O\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Burn leavened bread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22416P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22416P\"></sup> as a thank offeringand brag about your freewill offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22416Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22416Q\"></sup>—boast about them, you Israelites,for this is what you love to do,”declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I gave you empty stomachs in every cityand lack of bread in every town,yet you have not returned to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22417R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22417R\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I also withheld<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22418S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22418S\"></sup> rain from youwhen the harvest was still three months away.I sent rain on one town,but withheld it from another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22418T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22418T\"></sup>One field had rain;another had none and dried up.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>People staggered from town to town for water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22419U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22419U\"></sup>but did not get enough<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22419V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22419V\"></sup> to drink,yet you have not returned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22419W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22419W\"></sup> to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22419X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22419X\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Many times I struck your gardens and vineyards,destroying them with blight and mildew.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22420Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22420Y\"></sup>Locusts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22420Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22420Z\"></sup> devoured your fig and olive trees,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22420AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22420AA\"></sup>yet you have not returned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22420AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22420AB\"></sup> to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“I sent plagues<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22421AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22421AC\"></sup> among youas I did to Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22421AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22421AD\"></sup>I killed your young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22421AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22421AE\"></sup> with the sword,along with your captured horses.I filled your nostrils with the stench<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22421AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22421AF\"></sup> of your camps,yet you have not returned to me,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22421AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22421AG\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22421AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22421AH\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I overthrew some of youas I overthrew Sodom and Gomorrah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22422AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22422AI\"></sup>You were like a burning stick<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22422AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22422AJ\"></sup> snatched from the fire,yet you have not returned to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22422AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22422AK\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Therefore this is what I will do to you, Israel,and because I will do this to you, Israel,prepare to meet your God.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He who forms the mountains,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22424AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22424AL\"></sup>who creates the wind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22424AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22424AM\"></sup>and who reveals his thoughts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22424AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22424AN\"></sup> to mankind,who turns dawn to darkness,and treads on the heights of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22424AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22424AO\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty is his name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22424AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22424AP\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Hear this word, Israel, this lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22425A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22425A\"></sup> I take up concerning you:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Fallen is Virgin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22426B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22426B\"></sup> Israel,never to rise again,deserted in her own land,with no one to lift her up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22426C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22426C\"></sup>”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to Israel:“Your city that marches out a thousand strongwill have only a hundred left;your town that marches out a hundred strongwill have only ten left.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22427D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22427D\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to Israel:“Seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22428E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22428E\"></sup> me and live;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22428F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22428F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>do not seek Bethel,do not go to Gilgal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22429G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22429G\"></sup>do not journey to Beersheba.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22429H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22429H\"></sup>For Gilgal will surely go into exile,and Bethel will be reduced to nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22429I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22429I\"></sup>”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22430J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22430J\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and live,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22430K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22430K\"></sup>or he will sweep through the tribes of Joseph like a fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22430L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22430L\"></sup>it will devour them,and Bethel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22430M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22430M\"></sup> will have no one to quench it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22430N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22430N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There are those who turn justice into bitterness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22431O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22431O\"></sup>and cast righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22431P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22431P\"></sup> to the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22431Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22431Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who made the Pleiades and Orion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22432R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22432R\"></sup>who turns midnight into dawn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22432S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22432S\"></sup>and darkens day into night,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22432T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22432T\"></sup>who calls for the waters of the seaand pours them out over the face of the land—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22432U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22432U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>With a blinding flash he destroys the strongholdand brings the fortified city to ruin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22433V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22433V\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>There are those who hate the one who upholds justice in court<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22434W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22434W\"></sup>and detest the one who tells the truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22434X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22434X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>You levy a straw tax on the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22435Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22435Y\"></sup>and impose a tax on their grain.Therefore, though you have built stone mansions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22435Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22435Z\"></sup>you will not live in them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22435AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22435AA\"></sup>though you have planted lush vineyards,you will not drink their wine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22435AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22435AB\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For I know how many are your offensesand how great your sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22436AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22436AC\"></sup>There are those who oppress the innocent and take bribes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22436AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22436AD\"></sup>and deprive the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22436AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22436AE\"></sup> of justice in the courts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22436AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22436AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore the prudent keep quiet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22437AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22437AG\"></sup> in such times,for the times are evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22437AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22437AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Seek good, not evil,that you may live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22438AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22438AI\"></sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty will be with you,just as you say he is.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Hate evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22439AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22439AJ\"></sup> love good;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22439AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22439AK\"></sup>maintain justice in the courts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22439AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22439AL\"></sup>Perhaps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22439AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22439AM\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty will have mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22439AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22439AN\"></sup>on the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22439AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22439AO\"></sup> of Joseph.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore this is what the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty, says:“There will be wailing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22440AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22440AP\"></sup> in all the streets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22440AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22440AQ\"></sup>and cries of anguish in every public square.The farmers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22440AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22440AR\"></sup> will be summoned to weepand the mourners to wail.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>There will be wailing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22441AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22441AS\"></sup> in all the vineyards,for I will pass through<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22441AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22441AT\"></sup> your midst,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22441AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22441AU\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Woe to you who longfor the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22442AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22442AV\"></sup>Why do you long for the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22442AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22442AW\"></sup>That day will be darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22442AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22442AX\"></sup> not light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22442AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22442AY\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It will be as though a man fled from a liononly to meet a bear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22443AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22443AZ\"></sup>as though he entered his houseand rested his hand on the wallonly to have a snake bite him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22443BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22443BA\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Will not the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22444BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22444BB\"></sup> not light—pitch-dark, without a ray of brightness?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22444BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22444BC\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“I hate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22445BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22445BD\"></sup> I despise your religious festivals;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22445BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22445BE\"></sup>your assemblies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22445BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22445BF\"></sup> are a stench to me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Even though you bring me burnt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22446BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22446BG\"></sup> and grain offerings,I will not accept them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22446BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22446BH\"></sup>Though you bring choice fellowship offerings,I will have no regard for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22446BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22446BI\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Away with the noise of your songs!I will not listen to the music of your harps.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22447BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22447BJ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But let justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22448BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22448BK\"></sup> roll on like a river,righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22448BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22448BL\"></sup> like a never-failing stream!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22448BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22448BM\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Did you bring me sacrifices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22449BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22449BN\"></sup> and offeringsforty years<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22449BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22449BO\"></sup> in the wilderness, people of Israel?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You have lifted up the shrine of your king,the pedestal of your idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22450BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22450BP\"></sup>the star of your god—which you made for yourselves.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Therefore I will send you into exile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22451BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22451BQ\"></sup> beyond Damascus,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, whose name is God Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22451BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22451BR\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Woe to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22452A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22452A\"></sup> who are complacent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22452B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22452B\"></sup> in Zion,and to you who feel secure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22452C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22452C\"></sup> on Mount Samaria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22452D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22452D\"></sup>you notable men of the foremost nation,to whom the people of Israel come!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22452E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22452E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Go to Kalneh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22453F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22453F\"></sup> and look at it;go from there to great Hamath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22453G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22453G\"></sup>and then go down to Gath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22453H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22453H\"></sup> in Philistia.Are they better off than<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22453I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22453I\"></sup> your two kingdoms?Is their land larger than yours?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You put off the day of disasterand bring near a reign of terror.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22454J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22454J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You lie on beds adorned with ivoryand lounge on your couches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22455K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22455K\"></sup>You dine on choice lambsand fattened calves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22455L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22455L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You strum away on your harps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22456M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22456M\"></sup> like Davidand improvise on musical instruments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22456N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22456N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You drink wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22457O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22457O\"></sup> by the bowlfuland use the finest lotions,but you do not grieve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22457P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22457P\"></sup> over the ruin of Joseph.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22457Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22457Q\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore you will be among the first to go into exile;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22458R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22458R\"></sup>your feasting and lounging will end.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22458S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22458S\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sworn by himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22459T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22459T\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty declares:“I abhor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22459U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22459U\"></sup> the pride of Jacob<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22459V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22459V\"></sup>and detest his fortresses;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22459W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22459W\"></sup>I will deliver up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22459X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22459X\"></sup> the cityand everything in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22459Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22459Y\"></sup>”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If ten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22460Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22460Z\"></sup> people are left in one house, they too will die.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And if the relative who comes to carry the bodies out of the house to burn them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22461AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22461AA\"></sup> asks anyone who might be hiding there, “Is anyone else with you?” and he says, “No,” then he will go on to say, “Hush!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22461AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22461AB\"></sup> We must not mention the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given the command,and he will smash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22462AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22462AC\"></sup> the great house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22462AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22462AD\"></sup> into piecesand the small house into bits.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22462AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22462AE\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Do horses run on the rocky crags?Does one plow the sea with oxen?But you have turned justice into poison<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22463AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22463AF\"></sup>and the fruit of righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22463AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22463AG\"></sup> into bitterness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22463AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22463AH\"></sup>—",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>you who rejoice in the conquest of Lo Debarand say, “Did we not take Karnaim by our own strength?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22464AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22464AI\"></sup>”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty declares,“I will stir up a nation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22465AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22465AJ\"></sup> against you, Israel,that will oppress you all the wayfrom Lebo Hamath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22465AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22465AK\"></sup> to the valley of the Arabah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22465AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22465AL\"></sup>”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22466A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22466A\"></sup> He was preparing swarms of locusts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22466B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22466B\"></sup> after the king’s share had been harvested and just as the late crops were coming up.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When they had stripped the land clean,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22467C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22467C\"></sup> I cried out, “Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, forgive! How can Jacob survive?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22467D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22467D\"></sup> He is so small!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22467E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22467E\"></sup>”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> relented.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22468F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22468F\"></sup>“This will not happen,” the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22468G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22468G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me: The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was calling for judgment by fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22469H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22469H\"></sup> it dried up the great deep and devoured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22469I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22469I\"></sup> the land.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I cried out, “Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I beg you, stop! How can Jacob survive? He is so small!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22470J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22470J\"></sup>”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> relented.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22471K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22471K\"></sup>“This will not happen either,” the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22471L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22471L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>This is what he showed me: The Lord was standing by a wall that had been built true to plumb, with a plumb line in his hand.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> asked me, “What do you see,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22473M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22473M\"></sup> Amos?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22473N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22473N\"></sup>”“A plumb line,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22473O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22473O\"></sup>” I replied.Then the Lord said, “Look, I am setting a plumb line among my people Israel; I will spare them no longer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22473P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22473P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The high places<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22474Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22474Q\"></sup> of Isaac will be destroyedand the sanctuaries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22474R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22474R\"></sup> of Israel will be ruined;with my sword I will rise against the house of Jeroboam.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22474S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22474S\"></sup>”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Amaziah the priest of Bethel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22475T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22475T\"></sup> sent a message to Jeroboam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22475U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22475U\"></sup> king of Israel: “Amos is raising a conspiracy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22475V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22475V\"></sup> against you in the very heart of Israel. The land cannot bear all his words.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22475W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22475W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For this is what Amos is saying:“‘Jeroboam will die by the sword,and Israel will surely go into exile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22476X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22476X\"></sup>away from their native land.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22476Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22476Y\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then Amaziah said to Amos, “Get out, you seer!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22477Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22477Z\"></sup> Go back to the land of Judah. Earn your bread there and do your prophesying there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22477AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22477AA\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Don’t prophesy anymore at Bethel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22478AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22478AB\"></sup> because this is the king’s sanctuary and the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22478AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22478AC\"></sup> of the kingdom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22478AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22478AD\"></sup>”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Amos answered Amaziah, “I was neither a prophet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22479AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22479AE\"></sup> nor the son of a prophet, but I was a shepherd, and I also took care of sycamore-fig trees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22479AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22479AF\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> took me from tending the flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22480AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22480AG\"></sup> and said to me, ‘Go,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22480AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22480AH\"></sup> prophesy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22480AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22480AI\"></sup> to my people Israel.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22480AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22480AJ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now then, hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22481AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22481AK\"></sup> the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. You say,“‘Do not prophesy against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22481AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22481AL\"></sup> Israel,and stop preaching against the descendants of Isaac.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Your wife will become a prostitute<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22482AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22482AM\"></sup> in the city,and your sons and daughters will fall by the sword.Your land will be measured and divided up,and you yourself will die in a pagan country.And Israel will surely go into exile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22482AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22482AN\"></sup>away from their native land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22482AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22482AO\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22483A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22483A\"></sup> a basket of ripe fruit.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“What do you see,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22484B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22484B\"></sup> Amos?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22484C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22484C\"></sup>” he asked.“A basket<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22484D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22484D\"></sup> of ripe fruit,” I answered.Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “The time is ripe for my people Israel; I will spare them no longer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22484E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22484E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“In that day,” declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “the songs in the temple will turn to wailing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22485F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22485F\"></sup> Many, many bodies—flung everywhere! Silence!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22485G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22485G\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Hear this, you who trample the needyand do away with the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22486H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22486H\"></sup> of the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22486I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22486I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>saying,“When will the New Moon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22487J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22487J\"></sup> be overthat we may sell grain,and the Sabbath be endedthat we may market<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22487K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22487K\"></sup> wheat?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22487L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22487L\"></sup>—skimping on the measure,boosting the priceand cheating<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22487M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22487M\"></sup> with dishonest scales,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22487N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22487N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>buying the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22488O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22488O\"></sup> with silverand the needy for a pair of sandals,selling even the sweepings with the wheat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22488P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22488P\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sworn by himself, the Pride of Jacob:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22489Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22489Q\"></sup> “I will never forget<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22489R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22489R\"></sup> anything they have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22489S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22489S\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Will not the land tremble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22490T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22490T\"></sup> for this,and all who live in it mourn?The whole land will rise like the Nile;it will be stirred up and then sinklike the river of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22490U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22490U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“In that day,” declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“I will make the sun go down at noonand darken the earth in broad daylight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22491V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22491V\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will turn your religious festivals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22492W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22492W\"></sup> into mourningand all your singing into weeping.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22492X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22492X\"></sup>I will make all of you wear sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22492Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22492Y\"></sup>and shave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22492Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22492Z\"></sup> your heads.I will make that time like mourning for an only son<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22492AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22492AA\"></sup>and the end of it like a bitter day.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22492AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22492AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“The days are coming,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22493AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22493AC\"></sup> declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“when I will send a famine through the land—not a famine of food or a thirst for water,but a famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22493AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22493AD\"></sup> of hearing the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22493AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22493AE\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>People will stagger from sea to seaand wander from north to east,searching for the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but they will not find it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22494AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22494AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“In that day“the lovely young women and strong young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22495AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22495AG\"></sup>will faint because of thirst.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22495AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22495AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Those who swear by the sin of Samaria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22496AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22496AI\"></sup>—who say, ‘As surely as your god lives, Dan,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22496AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22496AJ\"></sup>or, ‘As surely as the god of Beersheba<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22496AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22496AK\"></sup> lives’—they will fall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22496AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22496AL\"></sup> never to rise again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22496AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22496AM\"></sup>”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>I saw the Lord standing by the altar, and he said:“Strike the tops of the pillarsso that the thresholds shake.Bring them down on the heads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22497A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22497A\"></sup> of all the people;those who are left I will kill with the sword.Not one will get away,none will escape.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22497B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22497B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Though they dig down to the depths below,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22498C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22498C\"></sup>from there my hand will take them.Though they climb up to the heavens above,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22498D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22498D\"></sup>from there I will bring them down.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22498E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22498E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Though they hide themselves on the top of Carmel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22499F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22499F\"></sup>there I will hunt them down and seize them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22499G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22499G\"></sup>Though they hide from my eyes at the bottom of the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22499H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22499H\"></sup>there I will command the serpent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22499I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22499I\"></sup> to bite them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22499J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22499J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Though they are driven into exile by their enemies,there I will command the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22500K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22500K\"></sup> to slay them.“I will keep my eye on themfor harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22500L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22500L\"></sup> and not for good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22500M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22500M\"></sup>”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22500N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22500N\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty—he touches the earth and it melts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22501O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22501O\"></sup>and all who live in it mourn;the whole land rises like the Nile,then sinks like the river of Egypt;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22501P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22501P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>he builds his lofty palace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22502Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22502Q\"></sup> in the heavensand sets its foundation on the earth;he calls for the waters of the seaand pours them out over the face of the land—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22502R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22502R\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Are not you Israelitesthe same to me as the Cushites?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22503S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22503S\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Did I not bring Israel up from Egypt,the Philistines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22503T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22503T\"></sup> from Caphtor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22503U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22503U\"></sup>and the Arameans from Kir?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22503V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22503V\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Surely the eyes of the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>are on the sinful kingdom.I will destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22504W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22504W\"></sup> itfrom the face of the earth.Yet I will not totally destroythe descendants of Jacob,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22504X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22504X\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“For I will give the command,and I will shake the people of Israelamong all the nationsas grain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22505Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22505Y\"></sup> is shaken in a sieve,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22505Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22505Z\"></sup>and not a pebble will reach the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22505AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22505AA\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>All the sinners among my peoplewill die by the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22506AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22506AB\"></sup>all those who say,‘Disaster will not overtake or meet us.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22506AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22506AC\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“In that day“I will restore David’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22507AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22507AD\"></sup> fallen shelter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22507AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22507AE\"></sup>—I will repair its broken wallsand restore its ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22507AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22507AF\"></sup>—and will rebuild it as it used to be,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22507AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22507AG\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>so that they may possess the remnant of Edom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22508AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22508AH\"></sup>and all the nations that bear my name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22508AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22508AI\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who will do these things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22508AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22508AJ\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The days are coming,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22509AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22509AK\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“when the reaper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22509AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22509AL\"></sup> will be overtaken by the plowman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22509AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22509AM\"></sup>and the planter by the one treading<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22509AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22509AN\"></sup> grapes.New wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22509AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22509AO\"></sup> will drip from the mountainsand flow from all the hills,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22509AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22509AP\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and I will bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22510AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22510AQ\"></sup> my people Israel back from exile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22510AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22510AR\"></sup>“They will rebuild the ruined cities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22510AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22510AS\"></sup> and live in them.They will plant vineyards<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22510AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22510AT\"></sup> and drink their wine;they will make gardens and eat their fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22510AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22510AU\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will plant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22511AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22511AV\"></sup> Israel in their own land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22511AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22511AW\"></sup>never again to be uprooted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22511AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22511AX\"></sup>from the land I have given them,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22511AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22511AY\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22511AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22511AZ\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;